"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"spaceInsetSmall"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic05SpaceB5Tokena","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"SpaceSemanticToken"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider\/spaceInsetSmall","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Has for value token DimensionRawTokens.outOfSystem50 (= 2)"}],"title":"spaceInsetSmall","type":"topic"},"ic_theme_orange.png":{"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesOrange\/ic_theme_orange.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"type":"image","identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","alt":null},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"kind":"symbol","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png"}],"type":"topic","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","title":"Theme Orange"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of badge"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"badge"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSBadge"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBadgeComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"code":"BadgeComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to expose the component tokens for ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"badge"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Badge"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of dimensions ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllDimensionSemanticTokensProviders"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"title":"OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider","role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemebadgecomponenttokensprovider"}}}